<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 06:14:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>监管举措令投资者不安后，中国游戏公司宣布股票回购</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-gaming-firms-unveil-share-buybacks-after-regulatory-move-unnerves-2023-12-26/</link><description>许多规模较小的中国游戏公司宣布了股票回购计划，这些计划被视为在市场因打击消费者游戏支出的监管举措而受到惊吓后试图安抚投资者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 05:49:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-gaming-firms-unveil-share-buybacks-after-regulatory-move-unnerves-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾军方发言人：菲律宾不会挑起南海冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-not-provoking-conflict-south-china-sea-military-spokesperson-2023-12-26/</link><description>菲律宾军方发言人周二表示，菲律宾没有在南海挑起冲突，以回应中国有关马尼拉侵犯北京领土的指控。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 05:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-not-provoking-conflict-south-china-sea-military-spokesperson-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>预计2024年中国将出现酷暑和更多极端天气</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expects-searing-heat-more-weather-extremes-2024-2023-12-26/</link><description>一位高级气候专家表示，中国正在努力应对有记录以来最冷的12月之一，明年由于厄尔尼诺天气现象，中国可能不得不迎接另一轮酷暑和极端天气的增加。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 04:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expects-searing-heat-more-weather-extremes-2024-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾选举前没有看到中国大规模军事活动的迹象</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-not-seeing-signs-large-scale-chinese-military-activity-pre-election-2023-12-26/</link><description>台湾国防部周二表示，在下个月的选举之前，台湾没有看到任何中国大规模军事活动的迹象，但正在密切关注中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 04:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-not-seeing-signs-large-scale-chinese-military-activity-pre-election-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国降息押注增加，亚洲股市走势不稳定，美元波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2023-12-26/</link><description>周二亚洲股市交易谨慎，而美元则潜伏在五个月低点附近，因美国通胀降温增强了美联储将很快降息的押注。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 02:30:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国警告火箭弹残骸将袭击南海</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-rocket-remnants-hit-south-china-sea-maritime-safety-authority-2023-12-26/</link><description>中国警告说，继十一天前第六次部署其最强大的运载火箭后，一枚火箭的残余物将于周二击中南海的一个地区。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 01:39:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-rocket-remnants-hit-south-china-sea-maritime-safety-authority-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>美元在清淡的贸易中难以站稳脚跟；日元稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-struggles-gain-footing-thin-trade-yen-steady-2023-12-26/</link><description>美元周二试图在假期清淡的交易中找到底部，因有迹象表明全球最大经济体的通胀正在降温，这可能会给美联储明年降息的空间带来压力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 01:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-struggles-gain-footing-thin-trade-yen-steady-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国将为在印度被捕的vivo员工提供领事协助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/china-provide-consular-assistance-vivo-employees-arrested-india-2023-12-25/</link><description>外交部发言人周一表示，中方将为印度当局逮捕的两名智能手机制造商Vivo中国员工提供领事保护和协助，并敦促印方不要歧视中国企业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 08:59:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/china-provide-consular-assistance-vivo-employees-arrested-india-2023-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国的圣诞节充满了闪闪发光的装饰和外国影响的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/christmas-china-brings-glittering-decor-foreign-influence-concerns-2023-12-25/</link><description>在中国大城市金光闪闪的购物中心里，装饰着灯光、金属丝和礼品盒的巨型圣诞树迎接着购物者，但在中国的许多地方，延长节日的问候是不可能的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 05:30:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/christmas-china-brings-glittering-decor-foreign-influence-concerns-2023-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体：菲律宾在南海的行动“极其危险”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-actions-south-china-sea-extremely-dangerous-chinese-state-media-2023-12-25/</link><description>中国官方媒体周一指责菲律宾多次侵犯中国在南海的领土、散布虚假信息并勾结域外势力滋事。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 01:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-actions-south-china-sea-extremely-dangerous-chinese-state-media-2023-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国地震死亡人数上升至149人，一周后仍有两人失踪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-earthquake-death-toll-rises-149-two-still-missing-after-week-2023-12-25/</link><description>中国近年来最强烈的地震之一横跨甘肃省和青海省，该地区居住着许多中国回族（一个紧密团结的少数民族）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 00:28:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-earthquake-death-toll-rises-149-two-still-missing-after-week-2023-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>北京打破七十年来的寒冷天气记录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-henan-province-hit-by-shortage-winter-heating-after-cold-wave-2023-12-24/</link><description>由于来自北极的刺骨冷空气，东北部部分地区气温达到-40摄氏度和华氏度。自12月11日以来，北京气象台记录了超过300小时的零下气温。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 06:56:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-henan-province-hit-by-shortage-winter-heating-after-cold-wave-2023-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>印尼镍冶炼炉火灾造成13名工人死亡、46人受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/smelter-furnace-blast-kills-12-indonesias-morowali-nickel-industrial-park-media-2023-12-24/</link><description>印度尼西亚青山不锈钢公司（ITSS）位于苏拉威西岛的镍冶炼厂所在工业园业主表示，周日，该公司旗下镍冶炼炉发生火灾，造成 13 名工人死亡、46 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 05:39:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/smelter-furnace-blast-kills-12-indonesias-morowali-nickel-industrial-park-media-2023-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>阿洛西离开布里斯班狮吼寻求“海外机会”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/aloisi-leaves-brisbane-roar-pursue-overseas-opportunity-2023-12-24/</link><description>布里斯班狮吼周日宣布罗斯·阿洛伊西辞去主教练一职，称这位前中场球员已离开俱乐部去寻找“海外机会”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 02:15:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/aloisi-leaves-brisbane-roar-pursue-overseas-opportunity-2023-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称八架中国战斗机越过海峡中线</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-eight-chinese-fighter-jets-crossed-straits-median-line-2023-12-24/</link><description>台湾国防部周日表示，在过去 24 小时内，已检测到 8 架中国战斗机以及 1 个中国气球飞越台湾海峡中线。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 01:38:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-eight-chinese-fighter-jets-crossed-straits-median-line-2023-12-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>